api_list.name: Generate PDF
api_list.description:
Generates PDF based on json input.
**Consider using Postman for testing,  since this platform does not return actual PDF file**
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://pdf-template-generator.p.rapidapi.com/pdf"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "pdf-template-generator.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
